Metadata: Sea Grant: Oregon State University Sea Grant College Program 1976-1977
program reports (annual, progress, planning reports, etc)

Annual report for the Oregon State University Sea Grant College Program for 1976-1977. Subjects include: Oregon's ocean, Fish for the future, Crabs on the range, Fish on the rocks, Farming the seas, New menu for salmon, Super oyster?, Medical progress for salmon and shrimp, Freeing fish disease-free, Microsporan mysteries, Ancient craft in fishing, From trawler to table, Canning seafood at home, Attack on microbes, Where buyer meets seller: bringing home the seafood, Aquaculture and economies, Lawyers at sea, Building on sea and shore.
